---
import DecoArt from "./DecoArt.astro";
---

<section
  class="relative overflow-hidden bg-brand-bg py-24 md:py-32 3xl:py-40"
  id="sobre-mi"
>
  <DecoArt
    variant="lotus"
    class="absolute left-[-10%] bottom-[-5%] z-[1] h-[300px] w-[300px] text-brand-gold opacity-[0.07] md:left-[-5%] md:h-[500px] md:w-[500px]"
  />
  <div
    class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_70%_50%,rgba(184,162,106,0.05)_0%,transparent_60%)]"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 md:px-8 2xl:max-w-7xl" data-parallax-el="0.05">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 items-center gap-16 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-24">
      <div class="relative mx-auto w-full max-w-sm lg:mx-0" data-parallax-el="0.07">
        <div
          class="absolute -inset-4 z-0 rounded-t-full border border-brand-gold/20"
        >
        </div>
        <div
          class="absolute -inset-2 z-0 rounded-t-full border border-brand-gold/10"
        >
        </div>

        <div
          class="relative z-10 aspect-[3/4] w-full overflow-hidden rounded-t-full bg-[#0a0a0f] p-1 ring-1 ring-brand-gold/30"
        >
          <div
            class="relative flex h-full w-full items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-t-full border border-brand-gold/20 bg-[#111116]"
          >
            <div
              class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 opacity-30 text-brand-gold"
            >
              <svg
                class="h-16 w-16"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1"
              >
                <path d="M12 2a10 10 0 1 0 10 10 H22 A10 10 0 0 0 12 2 Z"
                ></path>
                <path d="M12 2a15 15 0 0 1 7 10H5a15 15 0 0 1 7-10z"></path>
                <path d="M12 22a15 15 0 0 0 7-10H5a15 15 0 0 0 7 10z"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="font-heading text-xs tracking-widest uppercase"
                >Tu Esencia Aquí</span
              >
            </div>

            <div
              class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#06060a] via-transparent to-transparent"
            >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="absolute -top-6 left-1/2 z-20 -translate-x-1/2 text-brand-gold"
        >
          <svg
            width="16"
            height="16"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.5"
          >
            <path
              d="M12 2L15 12L22 15L15 18L12 28L9 18L2 15L9 12Z"
              fill="currentColor"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-3 -left-3 z-20 text-brand-gold/60">
          <svg
            width="24"
            height="24"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.5"
          >
            <path d="M12 2L15 12L22 15L15 18L12 28L9 18L2 15L9 12Z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-3 -right-3 z-20 text-brand-gold/60">
          <svg
            width="24"
            height="24"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.5"
          >
            <path d="M12 2L15 12L22 15L15 18L12 28L9 18L2 15L9 12Z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col text-center lg:text-left" data-parallax-el="0.03">
        <h3
          class="mb-4 font-heading text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-brand-gold/60"
        >
          La Sacerdotisa
        </h3>

        <h2
          class="mb-6 font-heading text-3xl font-light leading-tight text-brand-text md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl"
        >
          Más que una lectura,<br />
          <span class="text-brand-gold italic">una revelación.</span>
        </h2>

        <div
          class="mb-8 flex items-center justify-center opacity-60 lg:justify-start"
        >
          <div
            class="h-px w-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent to-brand-gold"
          >
          </div>
          <span class="mx-3 text-brand-gold">✦</span>
          <div
            class="h-px w-24 bg-gradient-to-l from-transparent to-brand-gold"
          >
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="space-y-6 text-sm leading-relaxed text-brand-text/60 md:text-base md:leading-relaxed"
        >
          <p>
            Bienvenidos a Tarot Divinidad. Este espacio no es solo un lugar de
            predicciones, sino un espejo para tu alma. A través de la simbología
            ancestral y la energía del universo, te ayudo a descifrar los
            mensajes que están esperando ser escuchados.
          </p>
          <p>
            Cada tirada es un portal hacia el autoconocimiento. Mi propósito es
            brindarte claridad en momentos de duda, iluminar tus sombras y
            empoderarte para que tomes las riendas de tu propio destino con
            intuición, fuerza y total confianza.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 flex items-center justify-center lg:justify-start">
          <a
            href="#servicios"
            class="group flex items-center gap-4 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand-gold transition-colors hover:text-brand-text"
          >
            <span
              class="h-px w-8 bg-brand-gold transition-all duration-300 group-hover:w-16"
            ></span>
            Ver nuestros servicios
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
